<h2 id="how-to-add-a-new-tag">How to add a new tag</h2>
<p>Please make sure to do the following for each tag:
&lt;!â€“-break-â€“&gt;</p>

<p>Create a .md file within <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_my_tags</code> folder with the name of your category, e.g. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">cool-stuff.md</code>. This file needs to look like this:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
2
